Wuhan epidemic affects the hearts of the Chinese people, "Henan hard core! " , "to Henan Copy Homework" and other topics linked to hot search, was many netizens hot discussion.

Behind this, it is a series of "excellent" measures to deal with the epidemic in Henan —— Foshan recently added 130 designated hospitals, 525 hospitals opened fever clinics, comprehensively checked Wuhan and even out-of-town Population, traffic fort temperature measurement, subway district disinfection, suspension of entertainment facilities, live TV broadcast, APP SMS push, Public Number Push, broadcast cycle, information bombing..

According to netizens, an aunt working in a village in Luoyang, Henan Province from Wuhan was told by the whole village not to go out. Village radio loop broadcast: "There are in Wuhan, try not to come back, where the New Year is the New Year. ". Feel it:

In addition, there are many "hard core" propaganda slogans.

In such a "hard core" anti-epidemic publicity work, even a netizen's grandfather did not let him go home... only willing to "airdrop" !

First Finance reporter noted that, a cluster of villages and towns in Xinmi, Henan Province, set off a flood -- Hello, folks! Receive Superior Urgent Notice, today is the second day of the first lunar month, please attach great importance to, do not go friends and relatives, more can not let outsiders to our village relatives, to avoid cross-infection virus. Let the villagers tell each other."

And in the group inside release group notice at the same time, the village head also in the group remind: The whole village after 10 o'clock, will completely block all into the village intersection!

Xinmi is a county-level city under the jurisdiction of Zhengzhou, the capital of Henan Province. January 26, the weather is gray, the air is scattered with snow. It was supposed to be a time to visit relatives and friends to celebrate the Chinese New Year, but because of the epidemic, few people go out at will, let alone pay New Year's greetings.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
To Send people to the high-speed railway station, the first financial reporter drove to Zhengzhou Railway Station on the 26th. Compared with the usual hustle and bustle of this time of year, this year's road traffic, pedestrians scattered. First Financial reporter driving along the road to see, and the main road connected to the village road, have set up artificial obstacles, forklift or car placed in the middle of the road, do not allow vehicles in and out.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Arriving at the high-speed Railway Station, the reporter noticed that the passengers were very conscious and protective, and seldom saw those who did not wear masks. On a large screen at a high-speed railway station, a CCTV news bulletin reads, "here comes the COVID-19, how to protect it. ".

On This Day, the Henan Provincial Government issued a circular on strengthening the prevention and control of pneumonia in COVID-19, calling for the effective strengthening of social management and the reduction of public gatherings, immediately stop public gatherings where there is a clear risk of cross-contamination.

"grassroots organizations in both urban and rural areas should fully play the role of big data and accurately manage people from epidemic areas such as Wuhan, " the notice said

The reporter also observed that for local villagers going out to work and do business, grass-roots organizations have all made strict statistics. Some people drove home from Jingmen, Hubei, a few days ago, and then went missing. The local government has also specially mobilized the masses to actively search for them, is to carry on the health registration, urges its home or the isolation medical observation 14 days, prevents the epidemic importation.

A "My village is heavily guarded" video, in Henan villagers in the group spread quite widely, the photographer intended to know all the villagers, cut off the transmission of the virus, do a good job of epidemic prevention and control.

On the Xinmi Government's website, there is an "open letter to Wuhan returning to the old people of Henan Province and compatriots from Wuhan to Henan" signed as "Henan COVID-19 pneumonia joint prevention and Control Headquarters" . "after January 10,2020, we invite our compatriots from Wuhan to come to Henan from Wuhan to assist us in the prevention and control of the epidemic so as to better protect the lives and health of the people in the province, " the letter said

The letter also proposes three measures for this group:

1. House isolation for 14 days;
2. When fever or cough occurs, wear a mask immediately and go to the fever clinic of the local designated medical institution designated by the Provincial Health and Health Commission
Third, do a good job of the protection of other family members, as far as possible not to participate in social activities, the home does not receive guests.

1. House isolation for 14 days;

2. When fever or cough occurs, wear a mask immediately and go to the fever clinic of the local designated medical institution designated by the Provincial Health and Health Commission

Third, do a good job of the protection of other family members, as far as possible not to participate in social activities, the home does not receive guests.

The reporter noted that despite the inconvenience, the villagers had little to say in favor of the measures taken by the government. The village chief has also been reminding the group that the fastest and cheapest way to deal with the outbreak is to isolate it at home for two weeks, which would have the least economic impact and be most beneficial to life and health. "staying at home is the best thing you can do for society. "

Not only the grass-roots, the city of Henan Epidemic Prevention propaganda work is also very effective. Miss Yao, from Luoyang, Henan Province, told China Business News that this year, families have canceled the traditional custom of paying New Year calls and even supermarkets won't let them in without masks.

On January 24, Zhengzhou's education bureau issued an emergency notice on strengthening the prevention and control of pneumonia among off-campus training institutions, calling for a complete suspension of extra classes during the winter vacation from the same day.

On the same day, Yinji international tourist resort also issued a temporary closure notice, beautiful rural Huanggu Temple Folk Temple Fair, Tianye Cave scenic Spring Festival temple fair will be cancelled accordingly.

On January 25, Xinmi Coach Center Station also issued an emergency notice. From January 26, all passenger services in the Coach Center Station will be suspended until further notice.

The Red Star News Commentary said Netizens had posted "measures" , including mass text messages from operators in the past few days, as well as propaganda about the epidemic in some villages, and even some villages urging those returning from Wuhan to "return. ". Mass texting, which seems to be "behind the curve, " is actually very effective. Many older people aren't adept at using wechat and don't notice the social media swipes, but they do take mass text messages from the authorities seriously. To prevent and control the epidemic, the government needs to communicate the effective measures (wearing masks, washing hands) to everyone.

The commentary said that compared with big cities like Beishangguang, Henan has a large rural population and people returning to their hometowns for the Lunar New Year. The ability to mobilize to the grass roots in such a short time shows that a relatively three-dimensional epidemic prevention system has been put in place.
